# Tests and docs

Any non-trivial scenario logic should include tests.

Prioritize tests for:
- intent execution
- status queries
- ambiguity resolution
- scene activation
- compound actions
- demo reset/replay

Keep docs updated when behavior changes.

Canonical docs:
- `README.md`
- `docs/architecture.md`
- `docs/intent-catalog.md`
- `docs/api-contracts.md`
- `docs/demo-script.md`
- `docs/acceptance-checklist.md`
